tourBios.carHigh:
Has two wins on the All-American Tour.

2013: T21 at the Dakota Dunes Open.

2012: Was the Dakotas Tour Player of the Year.
tourBios.personal: Won high school state basketball championship at Norman High School in Oklahoma.

dyn.dynBios: Son of famous wrestler Andre Metzger, Sr....Favorite course is Oakmont...Dream foursome would be Tiger Woods, Jack Nicklaus and Graeme McDowell...Favorite quote is "Be a sponge of knowledge and a filter of information", Favorite sports teams are Oklahoma Sooner and San Francisco 49ers
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T21st in 2013 at the Dakota Dunes Open presented by SASKTEL.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T88th in Par Breakers on the PGA TOUR Canada.
